### Delete one joke
DELETE {{host}}/jokes/{{joke1}} HTTP/1.1
Accept: application/json

### Get all scores
GET {{host}}/scores HTTP/1.1
Accept: application/json

### Create one score
POST {{host}}/scores HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "test",
    "date": "2022-01-02T13:26:15.457+00:00",
    "score": 1,
    "joke": "{{joke1}}"
}

